# Personal, per-developer agent instructions
CLAUDE.local.md

# Per-directory agent instructions are set up by `cargo xtask setup-agents`,
# which walks the repo and, for every README it finds, creates symlinks in the
# same directory from CLAUDE.md and AGENTS.md to the README. This effectively
# allows agents to use the READMEs as their CLAUDE.md/AGENTS.md, while we keep
# everything in READMEs. The not-ignored root CLAUDE.md and AGENTS.md only exist
# to tell agents about `cargo xtask setup-agents` and point to the root README.
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
!/CLAUDE.md
!/AGENTS.md
